Use of your Personal Information
KKZAP collects and uses your personal information to operate its websites and deliver the services you have requested. We may also use your personally identifiable information to inform you of other products or services available from data system and its affiliates. Usually, KKZAP will contact you by e-mail or phone in 7 workdays. Sometimes, we may also contact you via surveys to conduct research about you opinion of current services or of potential new services that may be offered.
KKZAP keep track of the websites and pages our users visit within these information which they are collected, in order to know and understand what kinds of products or services are the most popular. This data is used to deliver customized content and advertising within KKZAP to customers whose behavior indicates that they are interested in a particular subject field. In addition, the personal information Users provide will allow KKZAP to send them messages regarding, among other things, new products, features, enhancements, special offers, upgrade opportunities, contests and other events of their interest. Users may also later opt out of these communications by sending us an email or simply just by uninstalling our Services.
Security of your Personal Information
KKZAP secures your personal information from unauthorized access, use or disclosure.
KKZAP will disclose your personal information, without notice, only if demand to do like this by law or in the good faith belief that such action is necessary to:
(a) Conform to the edicts of the law or comply with legal process served on KKZAP or the site;
(b) Protect and defend the rights or property of KKZAP;
(c) And, act under exigent circumstances to protect the personal safety, or the public.
Infrequency, we can share data with trusted partners to help perform statistical analysis, send you email or personal mail, provide customer support, or arrange for deliveries. Meanwhile, KKZAP guarantees that they do not sell, rent or lease its customer lists to third parties. All such third parties are prohibited from using your personal information and we are required to maintain the confidentiality of your information.
Analytics, Advertising and Other Services Provided by Other Companies
We may allow other third parties companies to serve advertisements in our Services, provide analytics services or other services for the Users experience. These companies may use cookies, web beacons, Users account information (that Users set up with these companies) and other techniques to collect information about you on our Services, other online services, like IP addresses, identifiers of your mobile device, conversion information, browsers usage and pages you have visited. This information may be used to deliver advertising and content according the Users interests, better understand of the Services usage from the Users and analyzing and tracking data. These third party companies may also share this information with their customers and clients. This Privacy Policy does not apply to, and we are not responsible for, third-party cookies, web beacons, or other tracking technologies.
Children Under Fifteen
KKZAP does not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under the age of fifteen. If you are under the age of thirteen, you must ask your parent or guardian for permission to use this website.
